title: Population of Luxembourg 2019 , by age
summary: In general Number of inhabitants has fallen over the Year.

Number of inhabitants is roughly constant from 20-24_years to 45-49_years, roughly increasing from 45-49_years to 50-54_years, roughly constant from 50-54_years to 55-59_years, and finally gradually decreasing from 55-59_years to 95_years_and_older.
The line significantly decreased by 2411.0 from Year 90-94_years to 95_years_and_older.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 5-9_years and 50-54_years.
Maximum Number of inhabitants, about 48111.0 was reported at Year 35-39_years
Minimum Number of inhabitants about 766.0 was reached at Year 95_years_and_older
